messages.text: Yes. Why are you texting me??
I’m lazy. Don’t wanna leave my room
You’re a worm you know that?
Want to bring your favorite little brother a sandwich?
Its just as far for you as for me, dumbass
Too far. Whyd they buy this place?
I don’t mind it. I don’t have to see you at least
Come on Al. How long will it take?
I’m not even asking for lettuce and tomato!!
If this is about a sandwich or some other stupid thing I swear to God Rory!!
It’s not Al. It’s this house. I hate it
Leave your room for once then
I’m in the den. Yell. I want to see if I can hear you
Yeah its like living in a giant prison or something
Or space. I thought I’d like it
Sometimes it feels like theres people here
Think about it. Its so big that we cant even yell and hear each other. How do we know there aren’t people in the other rooms?
People. Living in our house. I think we’d notice. Stop trying to scare me. Idiot
They could just move ahead of us. Be really clean. We’d never know
What? Are you in the house? Are you here?
This morning I was headed to the bathroom and I usually cut through this one room. Like a book room or something
It was locked. Its never been locked
So what. Mom or Dad locked it. Probably didn’t want you in there
The other people in the house. The ones moving in
I went to the other side of the room. In the hall where the bathroom is. It was locked too.
I’m done with this convo. Bye bye little brother.
Ya. It was one that I always walked past in the hall to my room. Today it was closed and locked. I checked the other door to it too.
There moving in. Taking over rooms
I don’t think so. But we should tell Mom and Dad huh?
I texted Dad. He LOLed it.
I found more. There connected to the other room. I think my bathroom is next
I think I only have the one
Ya. Your right. Theres more rooms locked up connected to the first room
I’m going to wait outside of one and listen
Mostly nothing. Then something weird. It was like a chair being moved. Like scraped across the floor. But for like an hour. And it wasn’t in the room next to me. It was deep in one of the other rooms
It could’ve been a pipe or something else
Me neither. Im with my friends
Come to my room when you get here. Through the house
Why? What happened? Is it okay????
Its all locked up. I can’t get from my end of the house to yours. I can’t even get in the kitchen!!!
Business meeting. Singapore. I sent him an email. No response. Probably thinks I’m being dumb as usual
Well maybe we should call the cops?
Laughed at me. Told me to get a key
Yeah. I guess we’re on our own
What? What’s going on over there?
Don’t leave your room. I left mine for maybe 2 minutes and it’s locked. They took it. I cant get back in
WTF is going on Rory? I’m leaving now
No, they’ll take your room too. I’ll come to you
ALANA!?!?! What’s going on? I’m outside. I’m coming
I didn’t want anyone coming out
I don’t think anyone is coming out
